INSERT [dbo].[AssociatedDocumentationCategoryPage] ([Id], [Content], [CategoryField], [Title]) VALUES (13, N'<p>By the default we at Dwarf development the company behind RokonoControl use MSSQL as our daily database solution, thus there are no need of any addition steps required participating in order to use the software with sql server. However if you want to get the latest version of the database in case you made any changes you can use the following command</p><p><br></p><p>dotnet ef dbcontext scaffold "yourconnectionstringhere;"&nbsp;Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer -o Models -f</p><p><br></p><p>Make sure to run the program inside the Platfrom folder to avoid corrupting the whole solution with redundant file</p><p><br></p><p>Deploying the database is easy, just go to our github repository and click on the <a href="https://github.com/KristiforMilchev/RokonoControl/blob/master/Platform/MSSQLGenerationScript.sql" target="_blank">MSSQLGenerationScript.sql </a> once you have opened the script go to your database client and paste the generation script then run the query, it will create the database for you, rhere i no need to setup a database in advabce,</p><p><br></p>', 8, N'MSSQL')
