INSERT [dbo].[AssociatedDocumentationCategoryPage] ([Id], [Content], [CategoryField], [Title]) VALUES (1009, N'<h1>Project Management</h1><p><br></p><p>We have built our tool around the agile project management methodologies, we took a deep study and feedback from several renowned project managers with over 20 years of experience in the field in order to bring the best practices in the agile field to our product. From the advanced planning boards, to the discussion boards for each work item, to personalized experience for each of the different members of your team we have built the perfect working environment. Build work item relations, attach diagrams, track teams, assign iterations and break up complicated tasks. You can do it all and much more, track all of your working using the powerful widget building system that allows team members to personalize a board, create their own widgets or use some of the ones that come with the platform by default.</p>', 7, N'341')
