g the user to add images for reference and a dropdown with all epics in the project where the user can suggest where he wants the feature to be added.</li></ul><p>The feature should be implemented in the system as a separate controller and the frontend components should be implemented as ViewComponents. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL)
