given user and he should have access to the corresponding channels that have the tag.</li></ol>', CAST(N'2020-05-22T22:57:41.503' AS DateTime), CAST(N'2020-05-22T22:57:41.503' AS DateTime), 1, NULL, NULL, 12117, 1, 1004, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, N'15', N'15', N'', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, CAST(N'2020-05-22T22:57:41.503' AS DateTime), NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL)
